OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy rain
OL,6,Fclearing away this evening then
OL,7,Fbecoming dry for a time. Further rain
OL,8,Fspreading east eastwards across most
OL,9,Fareas during the early hours. Drier
OL,10,Facross northwest Argyll later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,13,Frain at times, though with some drier
OL,14,Fspells too. Some heavier rain later in
OL,15,Fthe evening, with strong winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
